<!--
  PhantomX Hexapod - Fully Expanded URDF
  Generated from xacro sources for Isaac Sim import.

  MESH PATHS: Meshes are referenced as relative paths (./meshes/*.STL).
  Place this URDF file one level above a "meshes/" folder containing:
    body.STL, body_coll.STL,
    connect.STL, connect_coll.STL,
    thigh_l.STL, thigh_l_coll.STL,
    tibia_l.STL, tibia_l_coll.STL

  In Isaac Sim URDF Importer: enable "Parse Mesh" and set the asset root
  to the folder containing this file so relative mesh paths resolve correctly.

  xacro properties used:
    connect_offset  = 0.02633
    thigh_offset_y  = -0.0645
    thigh_offset_z  = -0.0145

  Joint limits (all revolute legs):
    effort=2.8  velocity=5.6548668  lower=-2.6179939  upper=2.6179939
-->
